INSTALLATION

  For example:

    # change to your website root directory
    cd /var/www/html

    # clone the git repository recursively
    git clone https://github.com/doxel/doxel-webapp --recursive

    # change the owner of the upload directory
    chown www-data.www-data doxel-webapp/upload -R

    # set permissions for the upload directory
    chmod 0755 doxel-webapp/upload doxel-webapp/upload/tmp


  You may have to adapt the above procedure for your environment or requirements.


CONFIGURATION

  You may edit upload related settings in doxel-webapp/php/upload.config.inc

